            {
              "sentence": "We recorded their wedding on video.",
              "translation": "我們給他們的婚禮錄了像。"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "I tried to call her, but all I got was a recorded message saying that she was away for the weekend.",
              "translation": "我每次給她打電話聽到的都是電話答錄機中說她外出度週末的錄音。"
            },
            {
              "sentence": "Was the concert live or was it recorded (= made before being broadcast)?",
              "translation": "音樂會是直播還是錄播的？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "definition": "to keep information for the future, by writing it down or storing it on a computer",
          "features": null,
          "translation": "記錄;記載;記下…備案",
          "examples": [
            {
              "sentence": "She records everything that happens to her in her diary.",
              "translation": "她把發生在自己身上的一切事情都記在了日記裡。"
            },
            {
